{
  "stem": "22447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But going through, I had the chance to go to Paris.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to see him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He sent his wife and his son, one boy, to Vichy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They registered as Catholics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were left alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One son was a doctor, so he went off to the American army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was left in Paris in his flat the whole war by himself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was his neighbors that looked after him, never gave him away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was there the whole war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not, not on that scale, not on the scale as it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't come across any Jewish people, apart from the one in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, I mean, you can't walk about saying in the square at night, though, and say, are you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't come across it, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, only that sign in Brussels where it said-- but the Germans put up, not the Belgians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans put it up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got that taken off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the, the order come through Friday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we moved off on Sunday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The army, they take their time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know how they are.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had to send an advance party to find the billet and sort out where we're going.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we, we got there-- we got there on a Sunday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you see people lying in-- on bunks in these hut sort of things, and all sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the first thing Monday morning, we all had to get a boost of a typhus.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was done by German nurses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The first-- when they were told they got to help out with the--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, this was in the training place.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
